title: NaTuLa
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Italian, Organic, Western, Salad bar, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Restaurant specializing in high quality, all-organic, additive-free ingredients. About half the menu is vegan/vegetarian, marked with a carrot symbol. Several items can be made vegan using soy milk mayo, vegan cheese, etc., if you ask the staff. Menu is in Japanese. Some staff speak some English.
